title: Sneak Peek! Watch Behind The Scenes Video Of Camila Cabello Filming A Music Video With Pitbull!
text:
2/18/2017 6:59 PM ET | Filed under: Anglophilia • Latinolicious • Music Minute • Pitbull • Twitter • Amazing • Fifth Harmony • Instagram • J Balvin • Camila Cabello 
One thing is for sure: Camila Cabello stays busy!! 
Related: Does 5H's Lauren Jauregui Have A Message For Camila? 
The singer teased the collab with a pic of the three of them together on her Instagram account (as you can see, above!) that she captioned "vroom vroom," but it's the leaked videos that REALLY have people talking!! 
Below, ch-ch-check out what is reportedly Camila and Pit Bull working together on a music video in this clip of leaked video: 
Camila and @pitbull filming their music video today (via @pitbull_updates ) pic.twitter.com/AwzdaAQjfu — Camren News (@CamrenNews) February 17, 2017 
Whoa!!! 
Related: Camila Has NEVER Had A Boyfriend! 
And there's more!! 
Here's a long clip of her dancing along with J Balvin in what is obviously a music video shoot (below): 
Camila and @JBALVIN on set for the music video (via groovemanmusic on Instagram) #2 pic.twitter.com/fupohXG9nW — Camila Cabello News (@CCabelloNews) February 18, 2017 
Nice!!! 
Gotta hand it to Camila - she's staying busy and keeping herself relevant immediately as she kicks off a solo career! Good for her!!
